{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"The most fun you can have offline","content":"<div id=\"attachment_4185\" style=\"width: 682px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/383380_347698125278305_146707288710724_862402_1645891238_n.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-4185 \" title=\"Me on a longboard\" src=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/383380_347698125278305_146707288710724_862402_1645891238_n.jpg\" alt=\"Me on a longboard\" width=\"672\" height=\"447\" srcset=\"https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/383380_347698125278305_146707288710724_862402_1645891238_n.jpg 960w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/383380_347698125278305_146707288710724_862402_1645891238_n-300x199.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 672px) 100vw, 672px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Me on a longboard</p></div>\n<p>I don&#8217;t even come close to the ridiculously photogenic guy, but justÂ <em>look</em>Â at that smile! Look at it! That is true joy. I&#8217;m as happy as a corgi on stilts as the internet would say.</p>\n<p>The photo is from a <a class=\"zem_slink\" title=\"Longboarding\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Longboarding\" rel=\"wikipedia\" target=\"_blank\">longboarding</a> class, organized by <a href=\"http://www.longboard.si/\" target=\"_blank\">Longboard Magazin</a>, I went to last Monday instead of nurturing an easter food hangover at home. I went again Â this Sunday, simply because the first one made me smile like <em>that</em>.</p>\n<p>My <a href=\"http://swizec.com/blog/seems-i-am-in-love-with-learning/swizec/2442\">first experience on a longboard</a> was a lot sillier than that photo:</p>\n<blockquote><p>Three days ago I was such a noob at this stuff it took me longer to get home from college than it would on foot.Â Now itâ€™s as quick as rollerblading (on my old skates) and getting faster. A lot faster!</p>\n<p>Thing is, I sort of jumped into the deep end with this.Â <a href=\"http://twitter.com/zidarsk8\">@zidarsk8</a>Â just showed me how to stop, I still canâ€™t brake, I can only stop. Sort of.</p></blockquote>\n<p>And <a href=\"http://swizec.com/blog/today-i-nearly-died-four-times/swizec/3251\">a longboard almost killed me</a> &#8230; four times &#8230; in a single day.</p>\n<p>But I love it! Longboarding is the single funnest thing you can do offline. From what I hear the only thing that might possibly compare is surfing, but that comes with all sorts of costs and traveling and other silly things that I don&#8217;t really have time for.</p>\n<p>A longboard is simple.</p>\n<p>You step outside, you live in an asphalt jungle, and you ride like the wind. It&#8217;s even better when you go on a longboarding trip for the whole day with a bunch of other <a class=\"zem_slink\" title=\"Newbie\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Newbie\" rel=\"wikipedia\" target=\"_blank\">noobs</a> and some guys who can show you how to use these things.</p>\n<p>You&#8217;re kind of tired the next day and you might have a sore knee or two &#8230; worth it! ðŸ˜€</p>\n<p>If you have a longboard at home, you should totally join us whenever the full day class is happening next. Well, I guess you&#8217;d also have to be from Slovenia, otherwise it might be a bit impractical.</p>\n<p>The whole first class was caught on video, but I&#8217;m told it&#8217;s been lost to science, so here are some cool photos instead:</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_4186\" style=\"width: 682px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/532741_347692488612202_146707288710724_862300_619788079_n.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-4186 \" title=\"Road cleanup\" src=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/532741_347692488612202_146707288710724_862300_619788079_n.jpg\" alt=\"Road cleanup\" width=\"672\" height=\"447\" srcset=\"https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/532741_347692488612202_146707288710724_862300_619788079_n.jpg 960w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/532741_347692488612202_146707288710724_862300_619788079_n-300x199.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 672px) 100vw, 672px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Road cleanup</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_4187\" style=\"width: 682px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/576025_347695228611928_146707288710724_862355_1226691061_n.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-4187 \" title=\"Learning to turn tightly\" src=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/576025_347695228611928_146707288710724_862355_1226691061_n.jpg\" alt=\"Learning to turn tightly\" width=\"672\" height=\"447\" srcset=\"https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/576025_347695228611928_146707288710724_862355_1226691061_n.jpg 960w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/576025_347695228611928_146707288710724_862355_1226691061_n-300x199.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 672px) 100vw, 672px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Learning to turn tightly</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_4188\" style=\"width: 682px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/534032_347697751945009_146707288710724_862396_809260405_n.jpg\"><img class=\" wp-image-4188 \" title=\"Turning at speed\" src=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/534032_347697751945009_146707288710724_862396_809260405_n.jpg\" alt=\"Turning at speed\" width=\"672\" height=\"447\" srcset=\"https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/534032_347697751945009_146707288710724_862396_809260405_n.jpg 960w, https://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/534032_347697751945009_146707288710724_862396_809260405_n-300x199.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 672px) 100vw, 672px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Turning at speed</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_4203\" style=\"width: 682px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://swizec.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/5444